<item>
            <title>[PAY-3821] Treasury: handle Worldpay SFTP failures in funding-batch send (alert once, stop run)</title>
                <link>https://wellfit.atlassian.net/browse/PAY-3821</link>
                <project id="10016" key="PAY">Payments</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Story.&lt;/b&gt; As an operations team member, I want the Treasury funding-batch send to alert and record context when the Worldpay SFTP transfer fails, so transport failures surface immediately instead of via App Insights archaeology.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Context.&lt;/b&gt; &lt;tt&gt;WorldpayFunding.SendFundingBatch()&lt;/tt&gt; calls the SFTP upload with no try/catch at any of its three layers; the 2026-06-03 SBOX failure (&lt;tt&gt;SocketException @ Renci.SshNet ConnectCore&lt;/tt&gt;) propagated raw &#8212; no alert, no failure state, no batch context. Full analysis + solution: &lt;tt&gt;bmad-wellfit&lt;/tt&gt; PR #2879 &#8594; &lt;tt&gt;_bmad-output/products/payments/04_ExpresseLane/enhancement/treasury-funding-send-error-handling/&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Acceptance criteria&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;AC-1: A send failure (&lt;tt&gt;LitleOnlineException&lt;/tt&gt; or &lt;tt&gt;SocketException&lt;/tt&gt;) does not propagate out of &lt;tt&gt;SendFundingBatch()&lt;/tt&gt;; error log carries BatchId, BatchFileName, SFTP host.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;AC-2: Exactly one alert email per failed run, enumerating the failed batch and every unsent batch (Id + filename); previously-sent batches excluded.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;AC-3: Run stops at first transport failure; all unsent batches keep &lt;tt&gt;RequestSentTimeStamp = NULL&lt;/tt&gt; (existing idempotent retry unchanged).&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;AC-4: A throwing alert email is swallowed and logged; original handling completes.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;AC-5: Happy path and existing empty-batch warning unchanged.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Tasks&lt;/b&gt; (&#8594; AC): T1 try/catch + unsent enumeration + guarded email (AC-1,2,3,4) &#183; T2 &lt;tt&gt;protected virtual SendBatchFile&lt;/tt&gt;/&lt;tt&gt;IsBankingDay&lt;/tt&gt; test seam (enables T3) &#183; T3 four unit tests per solution.md (AC-1&#8211;5) &#183; T4 env-level QA per solution.md recipe (AC-1&#8211;3).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Dependencies.&lt;/b&gt; None hard. Coordinate with 
    &lt;span class=&quot;jira-issue-macro resolved&quot; data-jira-key=&quot;PAY-3587&quot; &gt;
                &lt;a href=&quot;https://wellfit.atlassian.net/browse/PAY-3587&quot; class=&quot;jira-issue-macro-key issue-link&quot;  title=&quot;Payments/Treasury: Encountering an error while processing the funding batch&quot; &gt;
            &lt;img class=&quot;icon&quot; src=&quot;https://wellfit.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/universal_avatar/view/type/issuetype/avatar/10303?size=medium&quot; /&gt;
            PAY-3587
        &lt;/a&gt;
