 H2 (BackgroundService outer-try) &#8212; overlapping ground, must not conflict.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Trunk readiness: GREEN&lt;/b&gt; &#8212; single-method change + seam, behavior-identical on happy path, no flags needed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;BMAD:&lt;/b&gt; product=payments &#183; expresslane=enhancement/treasury-funding-send-error-handling &#183; docs PR #2879&lt;/p&gt;</description>
